Default is no parent (empty or -). ## The identity above is used for resolving the reference so it must be specified. # # parent: - # ## Adds a prefix to the identity of cells to make sure they do not collide with existing cells (whose ## IDs are numbers from 0..n, sometimes with a GUID prefix in the context of realtime collaboration). ## Default is csvimport-. # # namespace: csvimport- # ## Connections between rows ("from": source colum, "to": target column). ## Label, style and invert are optional. targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias(date_time_date,1s),
  demand AS metric,
  delay,
  loss
FROM flowcharting
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(date_time_date)
GROUP BY 1,2
ORDER BY $__timeGroup(date_time_date,1s)

SELECT
  srcIP AS "Source(0-99)",
  dstIP AS "Destination(0-99)",
  flow AS "Flow/kB"
FROM traffic
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(date_time_date)
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY $__timeGroup(date_time_date,1s)
